node.text:
Hey StarReaders! 😉 ⭐ 
We hope you didn't miss our first & second episode from the Star Stable Master Class with author @helenadahlgrenofficial. Here's the first episode for you to learn from now or save for later, to enjoy during your cozy weekend! 📖

If you've already dived into our Star Stable Master Class, we're happy to let you know that Episodes 3 & 4 will come out soon, stay tuned! 🤩

Not only is this Star Stable Master Class full of awesome advice, but we hope it encourages you to write your own story! Put your learnings to the test by joining our ongoing storytelling challenge. Take part in our short
story competition for the chance to have your story turned into an
Instagram comic by illustrator Elli Puukangaas! @ellipuukangas #SSOStoryTellers #ReadWriteUnite

node.title: Star Stable Master Class: From reader to writer

Ready, set, bake! 🍰 What is a birthday celebration without cake? That is where you come in! We challenge you to create a Star Stable birthday themed cake for this very special occasion. ⭐ We'll be selecting 10 brilliant bakers for this challenge. The winners  will not only be reposted on our social media channels but also win the exceptional #SSO10 box! As you can see above, it's filled with lots of lovely gifts for you to enjoy and remember such a milestone. 

The winners will each receive a Star Stable tote bag, baseball hat, stickers, fake tattoos, popsocket, pin badges, mousepad, yoyo, playing cards, sunglasses, balloons, mug, poster, Limited edition 10th Anniversary Vinyl, HyperX Cloud Alpha headphones (@hyperx), a selection of candy and a Star Stable gift card for 3 months free Star Rider (estimated total prize value $350 USD). 

Do you have what it bakes? 😉 🍰 Use the hashtag #SSO10 and #SSO10BdayCake to share your entry!

Hey StarFam! We're throwing a four-week anniversary extravaganza that will transform Jorvik into one big birthday bash. Look for updates as we announce the fun stuff we have planned to make this a memorable occasion for everyone.

In today's update: Ride to the event area in Moorland to party with us. Set off fireworks, play onstage, get yummy cakes for yourself and your horse, and buy cool decorations at Mel's costume shop! DJ Kai will get everyone dancing at this 24/7 party. Drop in whenever!

Speak to Gary Goldtooth to get your free Soul Steed! Talk to the Birthday Girl in the party area to start the hunt for golden horseshoes. Return enough of them to her, and she'll reward you with items from the Pandoric-themed Birthday Set. For more adventure, take the Quiz Walk to get ten additional free items.

Every day until the end of the celebrations, you can earn extra XP for racing! Check the race board in the party area each day to find out where that day's event is happening. Head over there, talk to the Birthday Girl, and GO!!

Rania Varanger, Madison, and Evergray are up for enjoying Jorvik with you. When you talk to them, they'll jump on your horse with you to join whatever shenanigans you come up with. Drop them off where you picked them up when you're done showing them around the island.

Keep on reading at starstable.com to find out more about the birthday celebrations!

node.text: They said making a game for girls was a MAD idea! Ten years, 180 countries, 14 languages, and 21 million registrations later, we say girls THRIVE in game worlds where they can be true to themselves. 🌟 On our 10th anniversary, we’re telling the world that Star Stable Online was never about empowering girls. Girls are strong! The game is about providing an inclusive, welcoming place where players are valued for being EXACTLY who they are and where they can make friends for life. To our community, the driving force behind Star Stable Online, this film is our tribute to your strength. ❤️ We want you to know that while we began this quest ten years ago, we’re only just getting started. #SSO10

Next up in Jorvik! 📣 We have some amazing content coming up for our birthday celebrations! Take a sneak peek at the exciting things on their way to Jorvik! 👀
#NextUpInJorvik

10th birthday!
Happy birthday to Star Stable Online! We’re celebrating 10 enchanting years with an epic party, a FREE horse, birthday items, freebies, and more!

Steve's Farm Revamp
Steve has been doing some redecorating and he’s almost ready to show off his hard work. And what better time for a grand reveal than the second week of our birthday celebrations?

New Coat Variations
Our third week of celebration brings SIX new coat variations! These coat colors have been highly requested so we’re bringing them to you all at once.

The Party is Still On
The horses arrive just in time to attend the party! DJ Kai will be on the dancefloor 24/7. Tired of dancing? Try sending ethereal lanterns into the sky or taking pictures at the photo booth!

Treasure Hunt and Chit Chat
There’s even more for week four! Are you any good at solving riddles? A treasure hunt awaits you and your friends. Mingle with the party guests for some chit-chat. Learn more about them and discover Jorvik lore!

(Featuring the brand-new song, "Celebration" by Dj Kai featuring Nomi, Lisa Peterson, and The Miscreants! @starstablerecords)
